{
  "info": {
    "name": "Staff & Inventory Management API",
    "_postman_id": "staff-inventory-api-v1",
    "description": "Complete API collection for the Staff & Inventory Management backend.\n\n**Setup:**\n1. Set the `base_url` variable to `http://localhost:5000`\n2. Run `POST /api/auth/login` with root/admin credentials — `token`, `user_id`, `shop_id`, and `active_shop_id` variables are auto-set\n3. All subsequent requests use the token automatically\n\n**Seed credentials:**\n- Root: root@org.com / Root@1234\n- Admin: admin@org.com / Admin@1234\n- Manager: manager@org.com / Manager@1234\n- Sub-Manager: submanager@org.com / SubMgr@1234\n- Staff: staff@org.com / Staff@1234",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
